description: Location: Mobile County, AlabamaSmokin' Gringos food truck is a fully licensed and self-contained restaurant on wheels, provide fresh and flavorful food in numerous locations throughout Mobile County.Serving killer Ala-Mexi-Cali grub all over town, our founders were influenced by the plethora of flavors and the spirit of the people found in the triangle of Alabama, Mexico and California.Bringin' fresh & flavorful grub to the people!Tacos, Quesadillas and then some!
name: Smokin' Gringos
